{"tid":1009427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夏威夷擬立法 未滿100歲不得買煙","createTime":"2019-02-05T07:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T00:59:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":729,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"835b06810ef410d4e78c4c9b93f5d6caf99e87b8","tid":1009427,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpjutwqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpjutwqj.jpg&h=0de643eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏威夷議會提出新法案，擬在2024年限制只有100歲以上才能買菸。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-05 14:27<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕夏威夷是美國針對抽菸立法最嚴格的地方，繼2016年成為首個將合法買菸年齡提高到21歲的州之後，議會如今又提出了新法案，擬在2020年將買菸年齡提高到30歲，並且隨後每年依序提高到40、50、60歲，到了2024年則是100歲以上才能買。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，本職為急診室醫師、連署此法案的夏威夷州眾議員克里根（Richard Creagan）表示，儘管知道抽菸是高度致命的事情，仍然有一群人對此嚴重上癮。<br />\n<br />\n若未來此法通過，將有效減少夏威夷商店貨架上的香菸，但遊客不會受到這條法律的限制，而且買菸禁令只限於香菸，不包括電子菸、雪茄或嚼菸。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦法律要求各州將購買香菸的最低年齡至少定為18歲，目前大多數州允許18歲的人賣菸，而有4個州將最低年齡提高到19歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2692347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2692347&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFlDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=94f07f77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2692347&h=9f87ad3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2692347</a>"},{"pid":"8080f3b06653a3eaa235f5aef83b34a1eb0ce1e4","tid":1009427,"uid":144,"like":8,"dislike":34,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"🚬"},{"pid":"a0212f5cafe5ec069aa19f527848d239cf9c3ff1","tid":1009427,"uid":43557,"like":171,"dislike":6,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:27:23.000Z","msg":"去旅行大手入貨賣俾市民fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb25a6fdc326652e6be72f38b3cc81d354